---
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<section class="relative overflow-hidden pt-12 pb-24 md:pt-24 md:pb-32 px-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop">
  <div class="max-w-container-max mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-20 items-center">
    <div class="z-10 relative">
      <div
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-primary-fixed text-on-primary-fixed text-label-sm font-label-sm mb-6"
      >
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">auto_awesome</span>
        IA de Bienestar Organizacional
      </div>
      <h1
        class="font-display-lg-mobile md:font-display-lg text-display-lg-mobile md:text-display-lg mb-6 tracking-tight leading-tight"
      >
        Convierte señales del equipo en decisiones oportunas.
      </h1>
      <p class="font-body-lg text-body-lg text-on-surface-variant mb-10 max-w-xl">
        Pulsi te ayuda a entender el pulso de tu organización en tiempo real, detectando señales de
        sobrecarga, tendencias y causas probables para actuar antes de que los problemas escalen.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
        <button
          class="primary-gradient text-on-primary font-label-md text-label-md font-bold px-8 py-4 rounded-full shadow-xl shadow-primary/25 hover:shadow-primary/40 transition-all"
        >
          Solicitar Demo
        </button>
        <button
          class="bg-white border border-outline-variant text-on-surface font-label-md text-label-md font-bold px-8 py-4 rounded-full hover:bg-surface transition-all flex items-center justify-center gap-2"
        >
          Ver Plataforma <span class="material-symbols-outlined">arrow_forward</span>
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="relative">
      <div class="macbook-mockup">
        <div class="macbook-screen overflow-hidden">
          <img
            alt="Pulsi Dashboard"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover rounded-sm"
            src={`${base}images/vista_dashboard.png`}
          />
        </div>
        <div class="macbook-base"></div>
      </div>

      <div
        class="absolute -top-6 -right-6 bg-white/90 backdrop-blur rounded-xl border border-outline-variant p-4 shadow-lg z-30"
      >
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-tertiary-container/20 flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-tertiary">trending_up</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="text-label-sm font-label-sm text-on-surface-variant">Bienestar</p>
            <p class="text-headline-lg font-headline-lg text-primary">7.8/10</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="pulse-line"></div>
</section>
